{"tid":1111986,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港蟬聯亞洲公幹最貴城市 日均逾4000元","createTime":"2019-04-17T07:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T14:11:16.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8d70c4228030cc377c92a331477230a358a96ac3","tid":1111986,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:32:30.000Z","msg":"人力資源管理顧問機構ECA International發表報告指出，香港連續兩年成為亞洲公幹費用最昂貴的城市，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">到港出差平均費用為每天515美元(約4017港元)</span></strong>，按年升超過1%。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港物價和服務費用昂貴，酒店住宿價格不菲</span></strong>，因此一直是亞洲公幹成本最高的城市之一，且與東京、首爾和新加坡等地的差距稍微擴大。亞洲城市中，東京繼續排名第2，平均每天使費494美元，首爾及新加坡分別排第3及第4。<br />\n<br />\n全球方面，紐約是全球公幹費用最昂貴城市，平均每日支出799美元，其次是瑞士日內瓦及蘇黎世；<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港全球則排名19位</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n報告涵蓋全球195個國家400個地點，分析公幹酒店房間、膳食、洗衣等各項支出。"},{"pid":"e408f1d12eb321938423ae51cf5ec89bdb9697ac","tid":1111986,"uid":35430,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"唔係喎，有駐港連登仔話香港物價好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5ca2b8f64afc7e877121797475be2cddece936","tid":1111986,"uid":224860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:19:47.000Z","msg":"包唔包entertainment叫雞先<br />\n香港叫雞出名平喎"},{"pid":"fd9edda5eaea740749f9509c3c107cbc32d6618c","tid":1111986,"uid":105715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e5ca2b8f64afc7e877121797475be2cddece936","tid":1111986,"uid":224860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:19:47.000Z","msg":"包唔包entertainment叫雞先<br />\n香港叫雞出名平喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:21:10.000Z","msg":"落轉bar 啲菲雞唔洗錢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33a472be896bd097b05dc3ae02b6e32dd25a7bd","tid":1111986,"uid":224860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd9edda5eaea740749f9509c3c107cbc32d661